This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for user comment moderation, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the use of attention mechanisms, which is a popular topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with issues related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social media (cs.SI), which are relevant sub-categories in this context.
